Finish Page (Import Shared Library Wizard)

Requires: Base Development System

Use this page of the Import Shared Library wizard to open the generated LabVIEW project library and view a report that summarizes the generation. Select Tools»Import»Shared Library to launch the Import Shared Library wizard.

This page includes the following components:

  • Open the generated library—Place a checkmark in this checkbox if you want to open the generated project library file upon completion of the wizard.
  • View the report—Place a checkmark in this checkbox if you want to open the generated report file upon completion of the wizard. The file opens in the default Web browser.
